may or may not include a "header" which consists of the xsize and the
ysize of the image, either as shorts or as longs. Specify that with this
variable, either 'short', 'long', or 'none' for no header at all (in
which case you should also set img-size). img-size int 0 If an IMG file without a header is loaded (e.g. img-header-type is
